commit.message:
feat(misc): changelog, misc;

- Added change log file.
- PD DataTables continued.

feat(templates): pd datatables cont;

- Keyboard control instructions.
- Started keyboard controls for KeyTable.

feat(templates): pd datatables cont;

- Table state fixes and improvements.
- More key controls.

feat(templates): pd datatables cont;

- Fix some visual issues with the table editor.
- Removed bad trim js calls.

feat(templates): pd datatables cont;

- Custom field and highlight masking.
- Fixed issue with filter placeholders.

feat(templates): pd datatables cont;

- Continued JS evaluation for PD schemas.
- Added max length for Edit Mode fields.

fix(templates,js,css): unsafe inline;

- Update pd datatables to work without unsafe-inline and unsafe-eval.
- Add script nonces;
- Add script integrities.
- Use BS classes.

fix(js,css): little fixes;

- Fixed issue with Flexbox in Edge with no defined width.
- Fixed issue with foreign key links including the new/updated pill text.

fix(js): firewall error;

- Handle firewall blocks.
- Extract support ID and output new message type.

feat(dev): flag feature;

- Add in old code behind deprecation.
- Add new config option to use non-deprecated feature.

feat(pd): grants js evals;

- Wrote the remaining js evals for Grants pd type.
- Fixed an issue with date and datetime pickers not allowing future dates.

feat(misc): changelog;

- Added change log file.
- Added more options to CLI sub command.

fix(lint): syntax;

- Pyright fixes.
- Flake8 fixes.

files.patch:
@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@
+Upgraded DataTables JS contributed library and extensions to latest (as of 2025.03.27) for Recombinant previews. Added various UX improving features:
+
+- Bootstrap 5 theme for the DataTables;
+- Responsive View;
+- Improved i18n;
+- Fullscreen;
+- Editing in DataTables;
+- General improved functional JS code.
+
+Must use the option `ckanext.canada.enable_pd_datatable_editor`
\ No newline at end of file

